# Latency probe service for measuring round-trip communication delay to the Teensy.
# Served by: teensy node (firmware, service ~/ping) / mock_teensy node.
# Called by: TeensyInterface or any caller needing to verify Teensy connectivity.

# --- Request (no fields; sending the request itself is the probe) ---
---
# --- Response ---
bool success                              # True if the Teensy clock is synchronized (received_time is non-zero)
builtin_interfaces/Time received_time     # ROS timestamp recorded on the Teensy at the moment the request was received (rmw_uros_epoch_nanos)
